H3.text: Falange was the name given to several political movements and parties dating from the 1930’s in which European country. SPAIN

A4.text: Falange Española (FE) was a Spanish fascist and national syndicalist political organization active from 1933 to 1934.

A5.text: The Falange Española held its first rally in the Teatro de la Comedia in Madrid on October 29, 1933.
